refactor: remove floating widget, fully superseded by popout window

The I18nFloatingWidget (bubble + panel attached to document.body) has
been fully replaced by the popout window approach (ItemView via
openPopoutLeaf). This cleanup removes all floating widget code and
replaces its remaining dependencies.

Changes:
- Delete src/ui/floating-widget.ts entirely
- Remove floating widget instantiation and refresh calls from main.ts
- Replace showDictionaryManager() fallback with showMainPopout()
- Remove 8 floatingWidget.refresh() calls from dictionary-manager.ts
- Replace checkThemeUpdate() floating widget re-show with popout refresh
- Replace floating-widget-based metadata editor navigation with an
  Obsidian Modal (new MetadataModal class)
- Remove stale widgetPosX/widgetPosY settings fields
- Update stale comments throughout

